and I will protect Ka-young
as she does so.

00:23:26.655 --> 00:23:28.448
Whether it be psychologically…

00:23:32.494 --> 00:23:33.703
or physically.

00:23:35.872 --> 00:23:38.083
I'm her knight in shining armor, you see.

00:23:38.583 --> 00:23:39.793
