Is it too much to ask you to do your job?

00:31:40.899 --> 00:31:42.901
I can't take any more of this crap.

00:31:43.443 --> 00:31:45.570
Ms. Jung Yeong-sun. What did you just say?

00:31:46.779 --> 00:31:50.533
